        <h2 class="heading-medium">The MOT Fraud Reporting service application cookies</h2>
        <p>The MOT Fraud Reporting service sets a number of cookies to remember what you have done on the site and what messages you have seen. </p>
        <h3 class="heading-small">Our cookies message</h3>
        <p>You may see a pop-up cookies message when you first visit the MOT Fraud Reporting service. We’ll store a cookie so that your computer knows you’ve seen it and knows not to show it again.</p>
